		<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://blog.cedricbonhomme.org/2014/01/09/pyhids-notifications-bitmessage/" rel="bookmark">pyHIDS: notifications Bitmessage</a></h1>
		<div class="entry-meta">
			<span class="entry-date"><a href="http://blog.cedricbonhomme.org/2014/01/09/pyhids-notifications-bitmessage/" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2014-01-09T07:44:32+00:00">January 9, 2014</time></a></span> <span class="byline"><span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://blog.cedricbonhomme.org/author/cedric/" rel="author">Cédric</a></span></span>		</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

		<div class="entry-content">
		<p>Il est <a href="https://gitorious.org/pyhids/pyhids/commit/d2e52bcccca60294fda35df48c02831752b445b4">maintenant possible</a> de s&#8217;abonner à une adresse Bitmessage qui recevra les notifications de <a href="http://wiki.cedricbonhomme.org/projects:pyhids">pyHIDS</a>. Vous pouvez jeter un œil à la <a href="https://bitmessage.org/wiki/API_Reference">documentation</a> de l&#8217;API de Bitmessage.</p>
